'''格利澤752'''是在[[天鷹座|天鷹座]]的一對[[聯星|聯星]]，這個系統距離地球大約19光年，相對而言是很近的<ref name="Linsky">{{cite journal
 |title        = Stellar Activity at the End of the Main Sequence: GHRS Observations of the M8 Ve Star VB 10
 |author       = Linsky ''et al.''
 |journal      = The [[Astrophysical_Journal|Astrophysical Journal]]
 |url          = http://adsbit.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/nph-iarticle_query?bibcode=1995ApJ...455..670L&data_type=PDF_HIGH&type=PRINTER&ext=.pdf
 |format       = PDF
 |date         = December 20, 1995
 |volume       = 455
 |pages        = 670–676
 |doi          = 10.1086/176614
 |last2        = Wood
 |first2       = Brian E.
 |last3        = Brown
 |first3       = Alexander
 |last4        = Giampapa
 |first4       = Mark S.
 |last5        = Ambruster
 |first5       = Carol
 |access-date  = 2010-06-20
 |archive-date = 2012-03-28
 |archive-url  = https://www.webcitation.org/66UcKWj0D?url=http://adsbit.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/nph-iarticle_query?bibcode=1995ApJ...455..670L
 |dead-url     = no
}}</ref>。這個系統有兩顆[[恆星光譜|M-型恆星]]，[[聯星|主星]]是[[視星等|視星等]]9等的''格利澤752 A ''，[[聯星|伴星]]是[[視星等|視星等]]17等的''格利澤752 B ''，但更常用的名稱是''[[VB_10|VB 10]]''。
這個恆星對形成[[聯星#天文雙星|天文雙星系統]]，彼此相距74角秒(～434天文單位) <ref name="Biesbroeck">{{cite journal
